nodes.text: The deep launchpoint transfer was the modern designation for the Rakata transporter complex in the Warlord's Deep in the Tomb, an ancient Rakata prison on the planet Belsavis. The Sith Empire took it over as a military outpost.
The deep launchpoint transfer is a Imperial-restricted transporter in the Tomb on the planet Belsavis in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic.
